Lisa Plenske main character is a girl from men's dreams, in fact it is quite pretty ugly. Despite this she will try to fight for his place in the world of cold and superficial fashion business.

As Lisa did not like the doll out of this world, at the very beginning will be forced to fight the prejudice of colleagues, teasing, malicious comments.

In time, her warmth and ability will come to the fore, allowing her to join the network of personal and professional relationship with the company.
